data.customers_say: Customers find the dog toy cute and fun, saying their dogs love it and it keeps them busy for long periods. The size receives mixed feedback, with some finding it big while others say it's slightly smaller than expected. Customers disagree on whether it's suitable for aggressive chewers, with some reporting it doesn't hold up well. The squeaker feature also gets mixed reviews, with some liking it while others report no sound when squeezed.

top_reviews.review_title: Durable except for the squeaky toy
top_reviews.review_comment: I bought this for my son's puppy. So far it's held up to his chewing. He's already gone through 3 different toys. The only downside (maybe I should have given it a 4 star) is the squeaky toy - it didn't last at all. Our pup LOVES the squeaky part so that's a bummer. Maybe another toy will work out better.

top_reviews.review_comment: My mallionois loves these toys. She's got big dog energy! My girl likes to nibble, play tug of war, or bring her stuffy to bed. It does not fall apart quickly, very durable, affordable, cute and will buy these on repeat to keep her happy. Thanks for such a great product!

top_reviews.review_comment: WOOF WOOF! Oh boy, I'm so excited to share my paws-itive review of these WOWBALA squeaky rope dog toys! First of all, they're SO BIG and FLUFFY - just the way I like them! The plush material is so soft and cuddly, I can't resist giving them a big ol' lick. And the squeakers inside? Forget about it, they're the best! I could squeak them all day long. But what really gets my tail wagging is the rope toy part. It's perfect for a game of tug-of-war with my hoomans and doggy sister and brother! They're nice and sturdy, so I can really put my teeth into it (in a good way, of course). And don't even get me started on the alligator design - it's so cute and fun! I feel like I'm wrestling a gator (in a totally safe and non-threatening way, of course). Overall, these toys are a doggone delight! I give them four paws up (and a tail wag) - they're perfect for any pup looking for a fun and durable chew toy. Woof woof!
